                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.11324/2606.11324v1/x5.png",
                "caption": "Figure 3:Planner-Grounder-Corrector (PGC) closed-loop framework.A single Embodied-R1.5 instance asynchronously serves all three roles, maintaining a minimal FIFO memory buffer. The example shows a milk tea preparation task: the Planner decomposes it into sub-tasks, the Grounder provides spatial grounding for execution, and the Corrector continuously monitors progress, triggering replanning upon failure.",
